data.description: Welcome to your dream home on a spacious corner lot! Step into the heart of the home, where an open concept kitchen awaits with sleek granite countertops and modern appliances. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the living room, creating an inviting space for family gatherings and socializing. Picture cozy evenings by the wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing a retreat for each family member. Additionally, the master suite features its own private bathroom, creating a serene oasis for relaxation. The game room awaits, complete with a closet that could easily transform it into a 5th bedroom if desired. Work from home or organize your tasks efficiently in the dedicated office space, offering privacy and tranquility. The home is adorned with tile and laminate flooring throughout, offering a seamless and easy-to-maintain surface. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
